casebody.data:
Wednesday, March 30, 1994

MERIT DOCKET

93-91. State ex rel. Cohen v. State Teachers Retirement Sys. of Ohio.

In Mandamus. On motion to adopt settlement agreed entry. The court having been advised that the parties have settled their differences, this cause is dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., AW. Sweeney, Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney and Pfeifer, JJ., concur.
